**Invocation of the Divine Lords of the Body**

Emit the Divine Lord of the Verdant Flower, Supreme Prime of the Great Origin;
the Brain Spirit, Essence-Root, Lord of the Mud-Pellet Chamber;
the Eye Spirit, Radiant Brilliance, Lord of Mystic Darkness;
the Nose Spirit, Jade Luminance, Lord of Spirited Firmness;
the Ear Spirit, Empty Leisure, Lord Who Roams the Heavens;
the Tongue Spirit, Pervading Destiny, Lord of Right Order;
the Teeth Spirit, Blade-Edge, Lord of the Thousand Arrayed—
the spirits of the face guard one another,
drawing back the hun and returning the po, never to falter.
Swiftly, swiftly, in accordance with the statutes and ordinances!

The Heart Spirit, Cinnabar Prime, Guardian of the Numinous;
the Lung Spirit, Luminous Flower, Lord of Void Numinosity;
the Liver Spirit, Dragon Mist, Lord of Contained Brightness;
the Gallbladder Spirit, Dragon Radiance, Lord of Heroic Clarity;
the Kidney Spirit, Mystic Brilliance, Lord Who Nurtures the Infant;
the Spleen Spirit, Ever-Present, Lord of the Hun’s Pavilion—
the Twelve True Persons of the Lofty Tower,
the essences of the five viscera, six bowels, and the body,
all reside within the heart, chanting the Heavenly Scriptures.
By day and night, visualize them, and you shall live forever.
Swiftly, swiftly, in accordance with the statutes and ordinances!

The Ninefold Numinous, Most Wondrous, White Jade Tortoise-Terrace, Golden True Myriad-Qi Primordial Mother;
the One True Heavenly Essence-Fluid Lord within the heart, named *Flying Life, Supreme Hero*;
the Wind-Returning, Chaos-Merging, Supreme Holy Mother of the Central Luminance, named *Initiating Pearl*;
the Two True Lords of the Stomach Cavity, *Firm Jade*, named *Congealed Feather Pearl*;
the Feminine One, Imperial True, Ninefold Radiance Holy Mother;
the Three True Lords of Essence and Blood, Primordial King, named *Yellow Tranquility, Mystic Child*;
the Great Maiden of the Dipper, *Arrayed in Orchids*;
the Four True Lords of the Liver, *Pure Brightness*, named *Bright Conveyance, Youth*;
the True Immortal Maiden of the Dipper, *Dark Ink Child*;
the Five True Lords of the Spleen, *Nurturing Joy*, named *Great Prosperity, Child*;
the Supreme One Divine Lord of the Dipper, named *Frequent Motion, Pearl*;
the Six True Lords of the Lungs, *Supreme Prime, Plain Jade*, named *Beam of the South, Youth*;
the Great Cavern, Imperial One, Supreme Plain, Revered Spirit Father, *Tranquil Mother Essence*;
the Seven True Lords of the Kidneys, *Mystic Yang*, named *True Radiance*;
the Eastern Bluegreen Emperor, *Carved Beam’s Edge*;
the Eight True Lords of the Gallbladder, *Merging Scenery*, named *Northern Terrace, Mystic Essence*;
the Southern Red Emperor, *Ever-Coming Awareness*;
the Nine True Lords of the Mud-Pellet Chamber, *Imperial Prosperity, Supreme Sovereign*, named *First Spirit, Origin*;
the Western White Emperor, *Manifest Peace, Fortunate Supreme Origin Father Lord, Uncle Fire King*, named *Left Returning Brilliance*;
the Northern Black Emperor, *Preserving Completion, Prosperous Supreme Origin Mother Lord, High Same-Born*, named *Right Returning Light*;
the Central Yellow Emperor, *Containing Divine Brilliance, Purple Plain, Left Origin Lord, Concealing Luxuriance*, named *Peaceful Arrival, Supreme*;
the Imperial Supreme One, *Heavy Darkness, Void*, named *Profound Solitude, None*;
the White Plain, Left Origin Lord, *Initiating Brilliance, Towering Luxuriance*, named *Golden Gate, Supreme*;
the Nine August Divine Lords, *Sun Bright Essence*, named *Multitude Eternal Life*;
the Yellow Plain, Central Origin Lord, *Round Flower, Yellow Luxuriance*, named *Great Expansion, Supreme*;
the Supreme Plain, Nine August Divine Lords, named *Bright True*;
the Orthodox Unity, Left Immortal, *Second Completion, Child, Imperial Guest*, named *Western Flower*;
the Three Plain Elders, *Rare Expansion, Supreme*, named *Spirit Born, Dao*;
the Orthodox Unity, Right Immortal, *Crooked Literature, One Radiance, Firmness*, named *Jade Harmony*;
the Mystic One Elder, *Forest Void Man*, named *Numinous Timeliness, Dao*;
the Left Eye Youth, *Flying Spirit*, named *Yang Brilliance*;
the Grand Tenuous, Little Youth, *Dry Scenery Essence*, named *Meeting Literature, Child*;
the Right Eye Youth, *Morning Infant*, named *Yin Essence*;
the Jade Emperor Lord, *Encountering Mound, Brahma*, named *Treading Prosperity*;
the Numinous Embryo, Central Origin True Essence-Soul, named *Primordial Lord*;
the Non-English Duke, *Mystic Origin Uncle*, named *Uniting Talisman, Child*;
the Embryo’s White Qi Lord, *Diligent Mystic Child*, named *Nurturing Supreme Life*;
the White Prime, Cavern Yang Lord, *Luxuriant Spirit Standard*, named *Mystic Yi, Absolute Knot*;
the Central Bluegreen Qi Lord, *Case Extending Prosperity*, named *Uniting Harmony, Infant*;
the White Prime Lord, *Vermilion Crystal*, named *Bright Master*;
the Joint’s Black Qi Lord, *Bestowing Coming Life*, named *Essence Supreme Gate*;
the White Emperor Lord, *Manifest Peace*, named *Western Flower Embryo*;
the Central Yellow Qi Lord, *Ancestral Brilliance, Chariot*, named *Spirit Without Limit*;
the Supreme One August Spirit, *Diligent Harvest*, named *Returning Meeting Prosperity*;
the Blood’s Red Qi Lord, *Chaos Separation, Child*, named *Uncle Treasure, Firmness*;
the Central Elder, *Principle Bright Beginning*, named *Mystic Measure, Minister*;
the Supreme One Essence-Soul, *Mystic Luxuriance, Child*, named *Flourishing Prosperity*;
the Central Director of Destinies Lord, *Spirit Ancestor*, named *Principle Numinous Lapel*;
the Primordial Lord’s Essence-Soul, *Preserving Valley Youth*, named *Bright Heaven*;
the Sun’s Director of Destinies, *Receiving Life Lord*, named *Dao Numinous*;
the Imperial True Essence-Soul, *Profound Terrace Born*, named *Observing Supreme Life*;
the Life Gate, *Peach Prosperity Lord, Child Dao Prosperity*, named *Uniting Extending Essence*;
the Heavenly Emperor’s Essence-Soul, *Principle Maintenance, Treasury*, named *Dharma Motion, Pearl*;
the Moon’s *Peach Prosperity Lord, Square Fullness Child*, named *Motion Beam*;
the Director of Destinies’ Essence-Soul, *Hair Knot*, named *Celebrating Mystic*;
the Mud-Pellet Chamber’s Heavenly Emperor, Three Ones Lord, *Elder Historian Hua*;
the August One’s Soul, *Ascending Return*, named *Imperial Child*;
the Three Ones, Imperial True, *Commencing Leather Essence*, named *Central Mystic Born*;
the Heavenly Emperor’s Recording Soul, *Illuminating Without Obstruction*, named *Vast Spirit*;
the Crimson Palace’s Central One, Cinnabar Prime Lord, *Spirit Motion, Pearl*, named *Child South Cinnabar*;
the Supreme Emperor’s Essence-Soul, *Yang Hall Jade*, named *Eight Numinous Lord*;
the Crimson Palace’s Assistant Minister, *Central Radiance, Firmness*, named *Four Transformations, Numinous*;
the Heavenly Emperor’s Nine Passes Soul, *Returning Fortune Dao*, named *Absolute Darkness*;
the Life Gate’s Yellow Court, Primordial King, *Elder Historian Origin*;
the Lung Section’s Youth, *Plain Brilliance*, named *Prime Flower*;
the Yellow Court Lord, *Beginning Bright Essence*, named *Prime Yang Prosperity*;
the Nine Prime True Men, *Restraining*, named *Three Yangs*;
the Yellow Court’s Lower Minister, *Returning Supreme Brilliance*, named *Valley Below Mystic*;
the Nine Souls Lord, *Mystic Essence, Nurturing Sun’s Central King, Red Scenery*, named *Concealing Leisure*;
the Lone Moon Mother, named *Numinous Plain Orchid*;
the Nine Souls Spirit, *Chaos Merging, Returning to the Three Sections, Eight Sceneries Spirit*.

The Thirty-Six Palace Lords of Generative Qi,
illuminating and relying on the Eight Sceneries, perpetually at peace—
vast rosy clouds intermingle with the gods, descending from heaven.
Visualize and ponder this without further repetition.

Reverently, I gather the true officials of my five limbs,
the five viscera and six bowels,
the seven regulators and nine palaces,
the twelve spirit chambers,
the four limbs and five constituents,
the sinews, bones, brain, and marrow,
the skin, flesh, blood, and vessels,
the nine orifices and the constructive and defensive qi—
the one hundred eighty numinous passes,
the three hundred sixty bone joints,
the one thousand two hundred forms and shadows,
the twelve thousand essences and radiant lights,
the three hun on the left,
the seven po on the right,
the three sections and eight sceneries,
the twenty-four spirits,
the thirty-six thousand person-spirits within the body—
I am the child of the Supreme Highest,
the grandchild of the Primordial August.
My head is crowned with the Vermilion Bird,
my feet tread the Dark Warrior,
my left presses the Bluegreen Dragon,
my right abides with the White Tiger.
May my heart be free from evil,
my liver free from illness,
my lungs free from treachery,
my kidneys free from death,
my gallbladder free from fear,
my stomach free from filth.
May my entire body be pure,
all evil kept at bay.
Let the officials and soldiers guide and lead,
the five spirits attend at my side.
Swiftly, swiftly, in accordance with the statutes and ordinances!

